    "innerText": "The Jargon Jar 2.0\n\nCLICK ANY CARD BELOW TO TRANSLATE CORPORATE POSTURE INTO STRAIGHT TALK.\n\nCorporate Speak\n\n“Leverage synergies across touchpoints”\n\nDA Translation\n\n“Make the parts work together.”\n\nCorporate Speak\n\n“End-to-end digital transformation”\n\nDA Translation\n\n“We fix what's broken and build what's missing.”\n\nCorporate Speak\n\n“Scalable solutions for your growth journey”\n\nDA Translation\n\n“It works now and won't fall apart later.”\n\nCorporate Speak\n\n“SEO-optimized content ecosystems”\n\nDA Translation\n\n“Your site shows up when people search. That's the goal.”\n\nCorporate Speak\n\n“Robust backend infrastructure”\n\nDA Translation\n\n“The stuff running quietly in the background so nothing crashes.”\n\nCorporate Speak\n\n“Holistic brand alignment”\n\nDA Translation\n\n“Your logo, site, and words look like they know each other.”\n\nCorporate Speak\n\n“Onboarding workflow optimization”\n\nDA Translation\n\n“Getting started without the runaround.”\n\nMANUAL REGISTRY\n\n“If you need a glossary to read your website, you've already lost them.”\n\n— Jargon Protocol",
    "outerHTML": "<div class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white p-8 md:p-12\">\n            <h2 id=\"jargon-heading\" class=\"font-headers text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-3 border-b border-gray-dark/15 pb-4\" data-en=\"The Jargon Jar 2.0\" data-es=\"El Tarro de la Jerga 2.0\">The Jargon Jar 2.0</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-signal-red uppercase tracking-wider mb-6\" data-en=\"Click any card below to translate corporate posture into straight talk.\" data-es=\"Haz clic en cualquier tarjeta para traducir la postura corporativa en lenguaje directo.\">Click any card below to translate corporate posture into straight talk.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\">\n                <!-- Item 1 -->\n                <div class=\"flip-card h-40\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('flipped')\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                    <div class=\"flip-card-inner structural-border\">\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-front bg-bone-white\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-signal-red mb-1\" data-en=\"Corporate Speak\" data-es=\"Lenguaje Corporativo\">Corporate Speak</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Leverage synergies across touchpoints”\" data-es=\"“Aprovechar sinergias en los puntos de contacto”\">“Leverage synergies across touchpoints”</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-back\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-primary-blue mb-1\" data-en=\"DA Translation\" data-es=\"Traducción de DA\">DA Translation</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Make the parts work together.”\" data-es=\"“Hacer que las partes funcionen juntas.”\">“Make the parts work together.”</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Item 2 -->\n                <div class=\"flip-card h-40\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('flipped')\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                    <div class=\"flip-card-inner structural-border\">\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-front bg-bone-white\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-signal-red mb-1\" data-en=\"Corporate Speak\" data-es=\"Lenguaje Corporativo\">Corporate Speak</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“End-to-end digital transformation”\" data-es=\"“Transformación digital de extremo a extremo”\">“End-to-end digital transformation”</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-back\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-primary-blue mb-1\" data-en=\"DA Translation\" data-es=\"Traducción de DA\">DA Translation</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“We fix what's broken and build what's missing.”\" data-es=\"“Arreglamos lo roto y construimos lo que falta.”\">“We fix what's broken and build what's missing.”</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Item 3 -->\n                <div class=\"flip-card h-40\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('flipped')\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                    <div class=\"flip-card-inner structural-border\">\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-front bg-bone-white\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-signal-red mb-1\" data-en=\"Corporate Speak\" data-es=\"Lenguaje Corporativo\">Corporate Speak</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Scalable solutions for your growth journey”\" data-es=\"“Soluciones escalables para su proceso de crecimiento”\">“Scalable solutions for your growth journey”</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-back\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-primary-blue mb-1\" data-en=\"DA Translation\" data-es=\"Traducción de DA\">DA Translation</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“It works now and won't fall apart later.”\" data-es=\"“Funciona ahora y no se desmoronará más tarde.”\">“It works now and won't fall apart later.”</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Item 4 -->\n                <div class=\"flip-card h-40\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('flipped')\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                    <div class=\"flip-card-inner structural-border\">\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-front bg-bone-white\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-signal-red mb-1\" data-en=\"Corporate Speak\" data-es=\"Lenguaje Corporativo\">Corporate Speak</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“SEO-optimized content ecosystems”\" data-es=\"“Ecosistemas de contenido optimizados para SEO”\">“SEO-optimized content ecosystems”</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-back\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-primary-blue mb-1\" data-en=\"DA Translation\" data-es=\"Traducción de DA\">DA Translation</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Your site shows up when people search. That's the goal.”\" data-es=\"“Tu sitio aparece cuando la gente busca. Esa es la meta.”\">“Your site shows up when people search. That's the goal.”</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Item 5 -->\n                <div class=\"flip-card h-40\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('flipped')\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                    <div class=\"flip-card-inner structural-border\">\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-front bg-bone-white\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-signal-red mb-1\" data-en=\"Corporate Speak\" data-es=\"Lenguaje Corporativo\">Corporate Speak</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Robust backend infrastructure”\" data-es=\"“Infraestructura de backend robusta”\">“Robust backend infrastructure”</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-back\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-primary-blue mb-1\" data-en=\"DA Translation\" data-es=\"Traducción de DA\">DA Translation</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“The stuff running quietly in the background so nothing crashes.”\" data-es=\"“Lo que corre silenciosamente detrás para que nada falle.”\">“The stuff running quietly in the background so nothing crashes.”</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Item 6 -->\n                <div class=\"flip-card h-40\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('flipped')\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                    <div class=\"flip-card-inner structural-border\">\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-front bg-bone-white\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-signal-red mb-1\" data-en=\"Corporate Speak\" data-es=\"Lenguaje Corporativo\">Corporate Speak</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Holistic brand alignment”\" data-es=\"“Alineación holística de marca”\">“Holistic brand alignment”</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-back\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-primary-blue mb-1\" data-en=\"DA Translation\" data-es=\"Traducción de DA\">DA Translation</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Your logo, site, and words look like they know each other.”\" data-es=\"“Tu logo, sitio y palabras parecen conocerse entre sí.”\">“Your logo, site, and words look like they know each other.”</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Item 7 -->\n                <div class=\"flip-card h-40\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('flipped')\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                    <div class=\"flip-card-inner structural-border\">\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-front bg-bone-white\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-signal-red mb-1\" data-en=\"Corporate Speak\" data-es=\"Lenguaje Corporativo\">Corporate Speak</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Onboarding workflow optimization”\" data-es=\"“Optimización del flujo de trabajo de incorporación”\">“Onboarding workflow optimization”</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flip-card-back\">\n                            <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold text-xs text-primary-blue mb-1\" data-en=\"DA Translation\" data-es=\"Traducción de DA\">DA Translation</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-bold\" data-en=\"“Getting started without the runaround.”\" data-es=\"“Empezar sin rodeos.”\">“Getting started without the runaround.”</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Pinned Note card for balance -->\n                <div class=\"bg-[#FCFAED] structural-border p-5 h-40 flex flex-col justify-between relative shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute top-2.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3.5 h-3.5 bg-signal-red rounded-full structural-border\"></div>\n                    <span class=\"text-[8px] font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest block text-center mt-3\" data-en=\"Manual Registry\" data-es=\"Registro Manual\">Manual Registry</span>\n                    <p class=\"text-[10px] leading-relaxed italic text-gray-600 text-center\" data-en=\"“If you need a glossary to read your website, you've already lost them.”\" data-es=\"“Si necesitas un glosario para leer tu sitio web, ya los has perdido.”\">“If you need a glossary to read your website, you've already lost them.”</p>\n                    <span class=\"text-[8px] font-bold text-right block\" data-en=\"— Jargon Protocol\" data-es=\"— Protocolo de Jerga\">— Jargon Protocol</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
