    "timestamp": "2026-06-20T08:02:18.801Z",
    "innerText": "The Archive: Field Notes\n\nThese are notes from real people. I keep them pinned.\n\nSasha Esposito\n\nMarriage and Family Therapy, Inc.\n\n“Anthony has a rare natural ability to step into the world of his client and tune into what is important to them. His guidance is a safe pathway through.”\n\nVictoria Buckholz\n\nJourney to the Center of Hope\n\n“Digital Allies has truly been a beacon of expertise and reliability. I wholeheartedly recommend them to any organization seeking a dependable and knowledgeable tech partner.”\n\nTao Wei\n\nTao Wei Designs\n\n“Working with Digital Allies is not just about achieving results. It is about experiencing the clarity of real collaboration — where questions get answered and decisions get made.”",
    "outerHTML": "<section id=\"field-notes\" class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20\" aria-labelledby=\"testimonials-heading\">\n\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n            <h2 id=\"testimonials-heading\" class=\"font-headers text-4xl font-bold mb-3\" data-en=\"The Archive: Field Notes\" data-es=\"El Archivo: Notas de Campo\">The Archive: Field Notes</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-sm\" data-en=\"These are notes from real people. I keep them pinned.\" data-es=\"Estas son notas de gente real. Las mantengo fijadas.\">These are notes from real people. I keep them pinned.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n\n            <!-- Note 1 -->\n            <div class=\"structural-border pinned-note p-8 text-center\">\n                <div class=\"red-pin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n                <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold mb-1\">Sasha Esposito</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-xs mb-6 text-signal-red font-bold\" data-en=\"Marriage and Family Therapy, Inc.\" data-es=\"Terapia Matrimonial y Familiar, Inc.\">Marriage and Family Therapy, Inc.</p>\n                <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed italic\" data-en=\"“Anthony has a rare natural ability to step into the world of his client and tune into what is important to them. His guidance is a safe pathway through.”\" data-es=\"“Anthony tiene una habilidad natural poco común para entrar en el mundo de su cliente y sintonizarse con lo que es importante para ellos. Su guía es un camino seguro.”\">“Anthony has a rare natural ability to step into the world of his client and tune into what is important to them. His guidance is a safe pathway through.”</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Note 2 -->\n            <div class=\"structural-border pinned-note p-8 text-center\">\n                <div class=\"red-pin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n                <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold mb-1\">Victoria Buckholz</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-xs mb-6 text-signal-red font-bold\" data-en=\"Journey to the Center of Hope\" data-es=\"Viaje al Centro de la Esperanza\">Journey to the Center of Hope</p>\n                <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed italic\" data-en=\"“Digital Allies has truly been a beacon of expertise and reliability. I wholeheartedly recommend them to any organization seeking a dependable and knowledgeable tech partner.”\" data-es=\"“Digital Allies ha sido un faro de experiencia y confiabilidad. Los recomiendo de todo corazón a cualquier organización que busque un socio tecnológico de confianza.”\">“Digital Allies has truly been a beacon of expertise and reliability. I wholeheartedly recommend them to any organization seeking a dependable and knowledgeable tech partner.”</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Note 3 -->\n            <div class=\"structural-border pinned-note p-8 text-center\">\n                <div class=\"red-pin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n                <h3 class=\"font-headers font-bold mb-1\">Tao Wei</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-xs mb-6 text-signal-red font-bold\" data-en=\"Tao Wei Designs\" data-es=\"Diseños Tao Wei\">Tao Wei Designs</p>\n                <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed italic\" data-en=\"“Working with Digital Allies is not just about achieving results. It is about experiencing the clarity of real collaboration — where questions get answered and decisions get made.”\" data-es=\"“Trabajar con Digital Allies no se trata solo de lograr resultados. Se trata de experimentar la claridad de una colaboración real, donde las preguntas se responden y las decisiones se toman.”\">“Working with Digital Allies is not just about achieving results. It is about experiencing the clarity of real collaboration — where questions get answered and decisions get made.”</p>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </section>",
