  {
    "id": "cap_mqm2kzz4_rihry5",
    "selector": "section#faq",
    "label": "Frequently Asked Questions Real question…",
    "tag": "section",
    "url": "https://digitalallies.net/",
    "title": "Digital Allies | Tech Services & Consulting for Small Businesses — Kingman, AZ",
    "timestamp": "2026-06-20T08:02:25.697Z",
    "innerText": "Frequently Asked Questions\n\nReal questions. Straight answers. No fine print.\n\nWhat exactly does Digital Allies do?\n+\nIs the consulting really free?\n+\nWhat is the No-Ghosting Guarantee?\n+\nDo you work with businesses outside of Kingman?\n+\nDo you do design work or just development?\n+\nWhat does AEO mean and why should I care?\n+\nHow do I get started?\n+",
    "outerHTML": "<section id=\"faq\" class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20\" aria-labelledby=\"faq-heading\">\n\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n            <h2 id=\"faq-heading\" class=\"font-headers text-4xl font-bold mb-3\" data-en=\"Frequently Asked Questions\" data-es=\"Preguntas Frecuentes\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-sm\" data-en=\"Real questions. Straight answers. No fine print.\" data-es=\"Preguntas reales. Respuestas directas. Sin letra pequeña.\">Real questions. Straight answers. No fine print.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n\n            <details class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white group\">\n                <summary class=\"p-6 cursor-pointer font-headers font-bold text-base flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-light-pink transition\" data-en=\"What exactly does Digital Allies do?\" data-es=\"¿Qué hace exactamente Digital Allies?\">What exactly does Digital Allies do?<span class=\"text-primary-blue text-xl ml-4 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\">+</span></summary>\n                <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-dark/10 pt-4\" data-en=\"I design, build, connect, and maintain technology for small businesses and nonprofits. That starts with design — websites, brand identity, menus, signage, pitch decks, and graphic assets — then extends into development, automations, integrations between your apps, SEO/AEO audits, and ongoing tech support. Think of it as a design-forward consultancy that also handles the technical wiring.\" data-es=\"Diseño, construyo, conecto y mantengo tecnología para pequeñas empresas y organizaciones sin fines de lucro. Eso comienza con diseño — sitios web, identidad de marca, menús, señalización, presentaciones y recursos gráficos — y luego se extiende al desarrollo, automatizaciones, integraciones entre tus aplicaciones, auditorías SEO/AEO y soporte técnico continuo. Piénsalo como una consultoría orientada al diseño que también maneja el cableado técnico.\">I design, build, connect, and maintain technology for small businesses and nonprofits. That starts with design — websites, brand identity, menus, signage, pitch decks, and graphic assets — then extends into development, automations, integrations between your apps, SEO/AEO audits, and ongoing tech support. Think of it as a design-forward consultancy that also handles the technical wiring.</div>\n            </details>\n\n            <details class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white group\">\n                <summary class=\"p-6 cursor-pointer font-headers font-bold text-base flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-light-pink transition\" data-en=\"Is the consulting really free?\" data-es=\"¿La consultoría es realmente gratis?\">Is the consulting really free?<span class=\"text-primary-blue text-xl ml-4 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\">+</span></summary>\n                <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-dark/10 pt-4\" data-en=\"Yes. Tech consulting, AI consulting, brand discovery, design consultations, and AEO/SEO reviews are all free. I do not charge for conversations or clarity. You only pay when I design or build something. All costs are quoted before work begins.\" data-es=\"Sí. La consultoría tecnológica, consultoría de IA, descubrimiento de marca, consultas de diseño y revisiones AEO/SEO son todas gratuitas. No cobro por conversaciones o claridad. Solo pagas cuando diseño o construyo algo. Todos los costos se cotizan antes de comenzar el trabajo.\">Yes. Tech consulting, AI consulting, brand discovery, design consultations, and AEO/SEO reviews are all free. I do not charge for conversations or clarity. You only pay when I design or build something. All costs are quoted before work begins.</div>\n            </details>\n\n            <details class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white group\">\n                <summary class=\"p-6 cursor-pointer font-headers font-bold text-base flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-light-pink transition\" data-en=\"What is the No-Ghosting Guarantee?\" data-es=\"¿Qué es la Garantía Anti-Fantasma?\">What is the No-Ghosting Guarantee?<span class=\"text-primary-blue text-xl ml-4 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\">+</span></summary>\n                <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-dark/10 pt-4\" data-en=\"If I take your project, I finish it. If something changes, I tell you directly. Going quiet mid-project is not part of my service model. You will always know where things stand.\" data-es=\"Si tomo tu proyecto, lo termino. Si algo cambia, te lo digo directamente. Desaparecer a mitad de proyecto no es parte de mi modelo de servicio. Siempre sabrás en qué punto están las cosas.\">If I take your project, I finish it. If something changes, I tell you directly. Going quiet mid-project is not part of my service model. You will always know where things stand.</div>\n            </details>\n\n            <details class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white group\">\n                <summary class=\"p-6 cursor-pointer font-headers font-bold text-base flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-light-pink transition\" data-en=\"Do you work with businesses outside of Kingman?\" data-es=\"¿Trabajas con empresas fuera de Kingman?\">Do you work with businesses outside of Kingman?<span class=\"text-primary-blue text-xl ml-4 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\">+</span></summary>\n                <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-dark/10 pt-4\" data-en=\"Absolutely. I am based in Kingman, Arizona, but most of the work I do is digital. I serve clients locally and remotely. If you have an internet connection and a problem worth solving, we can work together.\" data-es=\"Absolutamente. Estoy basado en Kingman, Arizona, pero la mayoría del trabajo que hago es digital. Atiendo a clientes local y remotamente. Si tienes conexión a internet y un problema que valga la pena resolver, podemos trabajar juntos.\">Absolutely. I am based in Kingman, Arizona, but most of the work I do is digital. I serve clients locally and remotely. If you have an internet connection and a problem worth solving, we can work together.</div>\n            </details>\n\n            <details class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white group\">\n                <summary class=\"p-6 cursor-pointer font-headers font-bold text-base flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-light-pink transition\" data-en=\"Do you do design work or just development?\" data-es=\"¿Haces trabajo de diseño o solo desarrollo?\">Do you do design work or just development?<span class=\"text-primary-blue text-xl ml-4 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\">+</span></summary>\n                <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-dark/10 pt-4\" data-en=\"Design comes first. I build websites, brand identities, menus, signage, social graphics, pitch decks — polished print and digital visuals that look like you meant it. Brand discovery sessions are free. Once the visual direction is locked in, I develop the technology to match. Design-forward consultancy that also handles the technical wiring.\" data-es=\"El diseño viene primero. Construyo sitios web, identidades de marca, menús, señalización, gráficos para redes sociales, presentaciones — visuales pulidos de impresión y digitales que parecen intencionales. Las sesiones de descubrimiento de marca son gratuitas. Una vez que la dirección visual está definida, desarrollo la tecnología para que coincida. Consultoría orientada al diseño que también maneja el cableado técnico.\">Design comes first. I build websites, brand identities, menus, signage, social graphics, pitch decks — polished print and digital visuals that look like you meant it. Brand discovery sessions are free. Once the visual direction is locked in, I develop the technology to match. Design-forward consultancy that also handles the technical wiring.</div>\n            </details>\n\n            <details class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white group\">\n                <summary class=\"p-6 cursor-pointer font-headers font-bold text-base flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-light-pink transition\" data-en=\"What does AEO mean and why should I care?\" data-es=\"¿Qué significa AEO y por qué me debería importar?\">What does AEO mean and why should I care?<span class=\"text-primary-blue text-xl ml-4 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\">+</span></summary>\n                <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-dark/10 pt-4\" data-en=\"AEO stands for Answer Engine Optimization. It is about structuring your content so AI assistants — like ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, and Siri — can find and recommend your business. SEO gets you on the search results page. AEO gets you into the AI's answer.\" data-es=\"AEO significa Optimización para Motores de Respuesta. Se trata de estructurar tu contenido para que asistentes de IA — como ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews y Siri — puedan encontrar y recomendar tu negocio. El SEO te pone en la página de resultados de búsqueda. El AEO te pone en la respuesta de la IA.\">AEO stands for Answer Engine Optimization. It is about structuring your content so AI assistants — like ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, and Siri — can find and recommend your business. SEO gets you on the search results page. AEO gets you into the AI's answer.</div>\n            </details>\n\n            <details class=\"structural-border bg-bone-white group\">\n                <summary class=\"p-6 cursor-pointer font-headers font-bold text-base flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-light-pink transition\" data-en=\"How do I get started?\" data-es=\"¿Cómo empiezo?\">How do I get started?<span class=\"text-primary-blue text-xl ml-4 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\">+</span></summary>\n                <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-dark/10 pt-4\" data-en=\"Call or text (928) 228-5769, email contact@digitalallies.net, or use the contact form below. Tell me what you are trying to do. I will reply with next steps, a cost range, or a quick question. Usually all three.\" data-es=\"Llama o envía un mensaje al (928) 228-5769, envía un correo a contact@digitalallies.net, o usa el formulario de contacto abajo. Dime qué intentas hacer. Responderé con próximos pasos, un rango de costos o una pregunta rápida. Generalmente las tres.\">Call or text (928) 228-5769, email contact@digitalallies.net, or use the contact form below. Tell me what you are trying to do. I will reply with next steps, a cost range, or a quick question. Usually all three.</div>\n            </details>\n\n        </div>\n    </section>",
